content: Hit a roadblock with the blockchain project. Security vulnerabilities popped up. Time to dive into the code and fix them. Also, had a coffee with a tech entrepreneur—got some killer ideas on AI's role in urban planning.
The AI urban planning side project is coming along. We're visualizing how city expansion might affect market trends. It's fascinating how everything's interconnected.

Just presented the AI-enhanced trading system at work. They're impressed with the ethical compliance layer. On the side, I'm refining the urban planning model with new data sets.
